column1: #Text=Despite a larger police presence at the Tottenham Court Road protest , the protesters and Scientologists were both peaceful .
#Text=Police officers , when asked if they had had any problems with the protesters , replied , somewhat jovially , " I ca n't really speak to you , the only thing I can say is ' No comment ' .
